solver.explanations.strategies

Class ExplainingObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.search.loop.lns.neighbors.ANeighbor
      • solver.explanations.strategies.ExplainingObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, INeighbor, IMonitorInitPropagation, IMonitorUpBranch, ISearchMonitor

    public class ExplainingObjective
extends ANeighbor
implements IMonitorInitPropagation, IMonitorUpBranch
    a specific neighborhood for LNS based on the explanation of the objective variable.

    This neightborhood is specific in the sense that it needs to compute explanation on a solution. Furthermore, the fixSomeVariables method creates and applies decision, so that the explanation recorder can infer.

    Since:
    03/07/13
    Author:
    Charles Prud'homme
